  <h3 id="installation-and-operation">Installation and Operation</h3>

  <p>The centrifuge effectively separates waste oil from contaminants, including fine particulates, water, residual fuel, and emulsions known as the 'rag layer'. This separation increased the recovery rate by approximately 20%, enhancing both efficiency and profitability.</p>

  <p>A pilot test confirmed that the DMPX-028 centrifuge achieved high-quality recovered oil, which is sold to re-refiners and used as heating fuel, improving the overall waste management process. The centrifuge serves as a reliable waste oil purifier, ensuring cleaner output.</p>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <h2 id="how-it-works">How the Waste Oil Purifier Centrifuge Works</h2>

  <div class="not-prose my-6">
    <figure class="img-cap-landscape">
      <img
        src="/images/shared/Disc-Centrifuge-Self-Cleaning-Animation-600.gif"
