    <li><strong>Metal Content:</strong> Combined Aluminum and Silicon decreased from <strong>881 ppm</strong> to <strong>222 ppm</strong>.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="https://www3.epa.gov/ttnchie1/ap42/ch01/final/c01s11.pdf">Ash Content:</a></strong> Reduced from <strong>1.17 wt%</strong> to <strong>0.09 wt%</strong>.</li>
