  <p>Installing the DMPX-028, a disc stack centrifuge from Dolphin Centrifuge, significantly improved the waste oil recovery process at the Guam-based facility.</p>

  <p>The centrifuge enhanced oil purity, increased recovery rates by 20%, and reduced annual costs by $380,000. These improvements led to more efficient operations and substantial environmental benefits.</p>

  <p>By adopting the <strong>DMPX-028</strong> centrifuge, <strong>Dolphin Centrifuge</strong> enabled the waste oil processor in Guam to achieve greater sustainability, lower operational expenses, and optimized waste management. This implementation highlights the effectiveness of disc stack centrifuges in transforming waste oil recovery in the maritime industry.</p>

